<!-- #        qty      watts       hours/unit    watt-hours
# coffee    10     1200       0.0666667     80
# toast      2     1300       0.0166667     22
# waffle     1     1200       0.05          60
# laptop     1     50         1             50
# laundry    1     400/2500   0.5/0.583333  1658 
